{"tid":1604823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"最大問題係勇武手足行動冇目標！","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:56:26.000Z","uid":182047,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"aac99b2d67acfc54b73960740ee8e5ada1c4b9ee","tid":1604823,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"先感謝所有前線勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少少意見，啱聽可推，唔啱聽屌少幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往大家出嚟行動，係有目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n612阻止立法會開會<br />\n71衝入立會<br />\n721搞中聯辦<br />\n次次都好明確<br />\n任務完成就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但近幾次出嚟，好似為出而出咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似尋日咁，有啲手足喺政總外掟玻璃，但個目的係咩？<br />\n好多日都係：出到嚟唔知做咩-&gt;popo集結-&gt;放狗-&gt;手足被捕<br />\n我諗好多手足都唔驚俾人拉，問題係咁樣值唔值？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都知如果我哋幾萬人full gear衝上前，popo係會驚，我都好想所有和理非變晒勇武，但抗爭咗幾個月，你要大部分唔勇武嘅人一兩日之內忽然勇武，係唔現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議大家以後每次都要定一個明確行動目標，做完就散/轉場<br />\n可以建議埋第二、第三、第四目標&hellip;&hellip;分散對方力量（情報可以有虛實，當然小心唔好呃埋自己人）<br />\n(呢幾個月嚟，有咩成就未unlock，大家都知唔需多講)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再好似之前咁，俾時間對家集結，俾對方睇定嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有勇武手足可以自己組隊打游擊，冇必要跟大隊<br />\n和理非大隊引開敵人注意，小隊可自由去其他區域行動<br />\n當然必要時又可以回歸大隊潛伏，神出鬼沒<br />\n咁先可以發揮游擊最大效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望終於有一次可以做到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵進我退 敵駐我擾 敵疲我打 敵退我追</span></span>"},{"pid":"009beba74894409f940ce8add2b353d0ffb57f20","tid":1604823,"uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"都係<br />\n<br />\n勇武可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/爱尔兰独立战争\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%88%B1%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B0%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%88%98%E4%BA%89&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=82a18eae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/爱尔兰独立战争</a>"},{"pid":"0f55435fbf08ce11f29fb38ddf2961adfe1fcccf","tid":1604823,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad1c5661b9e690bb04057be30389c4d5f7ed494","tid":1604823,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"徵哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/pigeonpatrol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpigeonpatrol&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=62cd5add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/pigeonpatrol</a>"},{"pid":"616f9cf1f177d0cee4d17d9a504631a549e28f1f","tid":1604823,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"e8f340e861fb932c914d42e8bf66a6606942e507","tid":1604823,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ad1c5661b9e690bb04057be30389c4d5f7ed494","tid":1604823,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"徵哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/pigeonpatrol\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpigeonpatrol&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=62cd5add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/pigeonpatrol</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"本來咁多哨兵channel點解要開多個？<br />\n<br />\n各位記得！太空電話！太空卡！<br />\n唔好係屋企附近範圍開機！"},{"pid":"5716860da3d38ba270c823b00c8496b56a6eb827","tid":1604823,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b572e0f62b0466cffa0875a687416950eb2c3b4b","tid":1604823,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"7f6c77b453de86399f15004eb952a69abb0ffff6","tid":1604823,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"要對家某數量既人受大傷<br />\n算唔算目標?"},{"pid":"b12fe9d247e99d502ef042dcb6355ed380c096f0","tid":1604823,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ce7263ac93ea12e8370cb53d728ecacd5805d8","tid":1604823,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd8586e98b965d5fe419ffae64f594f1bca533dc","tid":1604823,"uid":76359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"目標- 各區 慶祝燈飾 旗仔 民賤建"},{"pid":"4b4b0031d92c649b02074ed3be099f7ac556f94c","tid":1604823,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f7c86adae0314b5bf3df2c24806b856cb228b05","tid":1604823,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"1d847c024ea60085cb8ea55db9137f86b5b9bf54","tid":1604823,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9c